{"type": "article", "id": 6460, "title": "生日快乐，《纽约客》", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2015-02-17T14:50:51Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1384, "name": "纽约客"}], "category": 12, "author": 13, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604224032Yqa2x9md5SgPjbsQ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<strong>New Yorker</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/culture/culture-desk/cover-story-nine-ninety?utm_source=tny&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=dailyemail&amp;mbid=nl_021615_Daily&amp;CNDID=27075598&amp;spMailingID=7508263&amp;spUserID=NzkzNjY1NzkwODUS1&amp;spJobID=621614753&amp;spReportId=NjIxNjE0NzUzS0\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nine for </strong><strong>Ninety</strong></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t如果你喜爱《纽约客》，最新一期的 90 周年特刊或许值得收藏。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t在即将进入第十个 10 年的时候，《纽约客》选择了从过去 90 年当中每 10 年选出一个封面，这 9 个封面共同构成了这一期杂志的封面。这些封面包括 Kadir Nelson 和 Anita Kunz 的油画、Roz Chast 等人的钢笔水彩画、Peter Mendelsund 的拼贴画等等。<strong><a href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/topics/90th-anniversary?utm_source=tny&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=dailyemail&amp;mbid=nl_Daily%20(M-S)%20(1)&amp;CNDID=27075598&amp;spMailingID=7524895&amp;spUserID=NzkzNjY1NzkwODUS1&amp;spJobID=622069131&amp;spReportId=NjIyMDY5MTMxS0\" target=\"_blank\">这里还有更多从档案库里整理的 90 年来的漫画、文章和评论。</a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t第一期的《纽约客》诞生于 1925 年 2 月。《纽约客》网站上这段由主编 David Remnick 主持的播客，也和编辑和作者们共同回忆了这本杂志的历史，以及这种独特腔调和风格自首任主编 Harold Ross 至今的形成和演变。它实现了自己当初的自我期许，充满「喜悦、智慧和讽刺」。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224026y3CRSDf1gE9FBe2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tKadir Nelson\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224027KgDq6bkV7uMlY4sR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tBarry Blitt\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224027TDpigEcwZ6ozSXJx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAnita Kunz\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060422402862xhXFAbN5PE9zQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tCarter Goodrich\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224029sd4h7rX3yfJaONmw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tLorenzo Mattotti\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042240308CgEB5Fb1eQ3uzxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tPeter Mentelsund\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224030ZUcIfyXsCj7Pv6Nz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tRoz Chast\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224031JSyhflPkCjGx28po.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tIstvan Banyai\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224031tM21IQCevlWi9KFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tChristoph Neimann\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这一期还有 Ian Parker 写的关于苹果公司设计总监 Jonathan Ive 和苹果设计实验室的一篇特写<strong><a href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/02/23/shape-things-come?utm_source=tny&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=dailyemail&amp;mbid=nl_021615_Daily&amp;CNDID=27075598&amp;spMailingID=7508263&amp;spUserID=NzkzNjY1NzkwODUS1&amp;spJobID=621614753&amp;spReportId=NjIxNjE0NzUzS0\" target=\"_blank\"> Jonathan Ive and the Future of Apple </a>。</strong><a href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/02/23/shape-things-come?utm_source=tny&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=dailyemail&amp;mbid=nl_021615_Daily&amp;CNDID=27075598&amp;spMailingID=7508263&amp;spUserID=NzkzNjY1NzkwODUS1&amp;spJobID=621614753&amp;spReportId=NjIxNjE0NzUzS0\" target=\"_blank\"></a>这篇文章中写到，过去的一年是他加入苹果公司以来经历的最艰难的一年，他患上了肺炎，而 Newson 的任命也似乎成为了他最终要离开的征兆。当环视这周围的一切时，他能够看到这间公司的未来，但也会想起过去。他依然会因为乔布斯的离开而难过。\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}